## Batch Format

The batch JSON MUST follow this schema exactly:

```json
{
  "name": "{BATCH_NAME}",
  "baseBranch": "main",
  "description": "Brief description of the batch",
  "assignments": [
    {
      "agent": "backend",
      "spec": "backend-{feature}",
      "specPath": "{OUTPUT_DIR}/backend-{feature}.md",
      "description": "Concise description of this agent's work",
      "round": 1
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## Rules for Round Assignment

- **Round 1:** Agents with no dependencies (shared utilities, designer tokens, backend schemas)
- **Round 2:** Agents that depend on Round 1 output (frontend consuming backend APIs)
- Same round = parallel execution. Two assignments for the **SAME agent** CANNOT be in the same round.
- Backend before frontend when frontend consumes the backend API.
- Designer before frontend when frontend implements designer's screens.

